ZH: 他亲自去接她。
EN: He personally went to pick her up.

ZH: 我亲自参加了会议。
EN: I personally attended the meeting.

ZH: 请你亲自给我打电话。
EN: Please call me personally.

ZH: 她亲自教我弹钢琴。
EN: She personally taught me how to play the piano.

ZH: 亲自做饭是最好的。
EN: Cooking by oneself is the best.

ZH: 亲自动手比较有成就感。
EN: Personally doing it gives a sense of accomplishment.

ZH: 他亲自去找了律师。
EN: He personally went to look for a lawyer.

ZH: 亲自体验一下才能理解。
EN: Only by experiencing it personally can one understand.

ZH: 他亲自给他儿子洗澡。
EN: He personally bathes his son.

ZH: 请你亲自去传达这个消息。
EN: Please personally convey this message.

ZH: 亲自出马就能解决问题。
EN: The problem can be solved by personally taking action.

ZH: 他亲自为她买了一束花。
EN: He personally bought her a bouquet of flowers.

