EN: Taking personal action can better control the situation.

ZH: 我亲自给他讲解了这个问题。
EN: I personally explained this problem to him.

ZH: 你亲自去拿吧，我没时间了。
EN: You personally go get it, I don't have time.

ZH: 他亲自给我写了一封信。
EN: He personally wrote me a letter.

ZH: 亲自处理这个问题最好。
EN: It's best to personally handle this problem.

ZH: 他亲自操刀完成了这个项目。
EN: He personally took charge and completed this project.

ZH: 请亲自核对一下这些文件。
EN: Please personally verify these documents.

ZH: 他们亲自去接机了。
EN: They personally went to pick up from the airport.
